fields.name: o_vehicle_model_year
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,

ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr))) AND LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr)) = '', NULL,

NOT ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr))) AND LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr)) != '' AND IS_NUMBER(model_yr) AND LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr)))=4, LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr)),

NOT ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr))) AND LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr)) != '' AND NOT IS_NUMBER(model_yr) AND LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(model_yr)))!=4, 'Unknown'


)
